{"type":"answer","id":45876,"parentType":"question","parentId":10544,"uid":4797,"contents":"很简单，在中国，熊和包子都是帝王的象征，熊是帝王的神兽，包子则专门用来喂熊。你吃熊心包子胆则犯下了弑君和篡位两大罪行。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/36ntmNn.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/36ntmNn.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/36ntmNn.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-07-05","agreeCount":8,"discussionCount":0}